application.pane

Interface PaneAnimator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PaneReplacer

    public interface PaneAnimator
extends PaneReplacer
    This interface gets two Panes, and creates a JavaFX Animations transition between them.

    Also:

    • Defines an PaneAnimator.AnimationType, to define the Animation types available to be used.
    • Defines a PaneAnimator.Handler to serve as an Animation EventHandler.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  PaneAnimator.AnimationType
      The type of Animation the user wishes to invoke.
      static class  PaneAnimator.Handler
      Use this Class as a EventHandler for handling JavaFX Pane switches and Animations.
